rfcs/0296-structured-logging.md
   502Ôćĺ### Don't break anything
   503Ôćĺ
   504ÔćĺAllow structured logging to be added in the current `0.4.x` series of `log`. This gives us the option of including structured logging in an `0.4.x` release, or bumping the minor crate version without introducing any actual breaking changes.
   505Ôćĺ
  1598Ôćĺ#### Build a serialization contract in `log`
  1599Ôćĺ
  1600ÔćĺInstead of internalizing a few serialization frameworks, `log` could provide a public common contract for them to conform to:
  1601Ôćĺ
  1602Ôćĺ```rust
  1603Ôćĺ// Instead of `Value::from_any` + `FromAny`
  1604Ôćĺ
  1605Ôćĺpub trait Visit {
  1606Ôćĺ    fn visit(&self, visitor: &mut dyn Visitor) -> Result<(), Error>;
  1607Ôćĺ}
  1608Ôćĺ
  1609Ôćĺpub trait Visitor {
  1610Ôćĺ    fn u64(&mut self, v: u64) -> Result<(), Error>;
  1611Ôćĺ    fn i64(&mut self, v: i64) -> Result<(), Error>;
  1612Ôćĺ
  1613Ôćĺ    ..
  1614Ôćĺ}
  1615Ôćĺ```
